## This Codebook is to describe all the the variables in order to help the reader to understand my code better

## mergedata: Merges the training and the test sets to create one data set.
## mean: mean for each measurement. 
## sd: standard deviation for each measurement. 
## trainpluslabel: bind activity_labels to the train data set
## testpluslabel: bind activity_labels to the test data set
## featuresnames: the names for all the features to be assigned to onedataset
## onedataset: This is the data frame that contains all the data
## subject: Each row identifies the subject who performed the activity for each window sample. Its range is from 1 to 30. 
